A Backbone.js Todo app using Play-scala,anorm and mysql.
It is the same Todo app found in Backbone.js examples


========================
HOW TO START THIS PROJECT
========================

* install sbt 0.13.5 if you do not have it already. You can get it from here: http://www.scala-sbt.org/download.html

* execute 'sbt' and then `help play` for play specific commands

* execute `sbt` and then `compile` to build the project

* execute `sbt` and then 'run' to run the built-in development server
